HEADWORD: Chophouse
<hw>Chop"house`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A house where
chops, etc., are sold; an eating house.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

